{"tid":834082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵通車】黃雨下西九站多處地方漏水","createTime":"2018-09-24T03:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T10:22:26.000Z","uid":117837,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"656305c7a0bfe19e75c9e3bc52fdbf5d5e8a491f","tid":834082,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537757765_9da0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537757765_9da0.jpg&h=4729cbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九站露天有蓋地方亦發現漏水，工人以水桶裝水。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n今天早上一場豪雨，高鐵西九龍站再現漏水。《蘋果》記者在B2層餐廳「堂前食坊」發現地下有大灘水漬及最少2處滴水，現場亦放了「小心地滑」的警告牌。由於食肆沒有上蓋，故不少途經行人都好奇水滴從何而降。有工人知道記者拍攝，不發一言，但用身體語言暗示，水滴很有可能是從天幕滴下來。另外，高鐵西九龍站頂層亦有兩處漏水。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537757840_3a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537757840_3a3c.jpg&h=6c6b71ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者發現西九站假天花出現漏水。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180924/58717204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180924%2F58717204&d=9V0snLNjGsSXGZAvKmetok%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c670d5e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180924%2F58717204&h=2b45d6aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180924/58717204</a>"},{"pid":"60c65bbd4095f38d9044784d93f28c4f739eb0a6","tid":834082,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffe